GF$F'F,I%X_BHGF$F'" }}}}}{SECT 0 {PARA 3 "" 0 "" {TEXT 321 33 " Biogeo
chemistry - Stoichiometry\n" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 319 46 "Stoichiom
etry of the biogeochemical reactions\n" }{TEXT 26 9 "d.sp.dt :" }{TEXT
 319 66 " rates of change of sp due to the sum of biogeochemical react
ions\n" }{TEXT 319 44 "note that rateX must be referred to as rX  \n" 
