degree celsius (cm^2/yr)\n" }{TEXT 26 11 "alphadata: " }{TEXT 319 59 "
temperature dependence of the diffusion coefficient (1/K) \n" }{TEXT 
319 88 "the in situ molecular diffusion coefficient, corrected for tor
tuosity is calculated as:\n" }{TEXT 319 75 "D(T,sal) = [(0.95-0.001*sa
l)* D(T=0,sal=0)*(1 + muc*T[C])]/(1-ln(por^2))  \n" }{TEXT 299 9 "exam
ple:\n" }{TEXT 300 37 "diffdata := [100., 304.,0.,0.,100.];\n" }{TEXT 
